reviewText: In order to appreciate these classics, one would have to remove themselves from today's technological, and acting standards. I enjoy the classics so these movies were exactly what I was looking for.

Apparently the February 2008 release of this set is a re-issue from the July 2007 set.  I gave it a 3 star blindly as I haven't seen the set but do know St. Clair's quality in general...  The titles include:

White Zombie
The Human Monster
One Body Too many
Invisible Ghost
The Phantom Creeps (movie version)
Death Kiss
Scared To Death
Black Dragons
The Corpse Vanishes

There is also 3 different 4-minute shorts - one a bio, one a poster gallery, and the last trailers.
